The paper deals with interference cancellation and transmission strategies in wireless networks, which are topics that fall under the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) categories. The use of multiple antennas and beamforming also suggests a possible connection to Multimedia (cs.MM) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) categories.
